flowchart TD
    A[Student opens Modules] --> B[System filters modules by student tier]
    B --> C[Student opens one module]
    C --> D[System loads lessons that match the same tier]
    D --> E[Student opens lesson]
    E --> F[System checks lesson tier and module tier access]
    F --> G{Access allowed?}
    G -->|No| H[Show 403 or deny access]
    G -->|Yes| I[Render lesson detail]
    I --> J[Show workbook if present]
    I --> K[Show video reference if present]
    I --> L[Show audio reference if present]
    I --> M[Show rich text content if present]
    I --> N[Show assessment placeholder if assessment_id exists]

    O[Sequential lock and watch progress automation are not active yet] --> I
